    <section name="Downloading and Installation">

      <p>
      Binary download of build 2579 are available for the Unix and 
      Windows platforms.
      </p>

      <subsection name="2579 Status">

      <ol>
        <li>Transit 2579 is nearing release.</li>
        <li>Magic 2579 is fully functional but lacks documentation.  The product is under 
            active development including possible API and configuration file changes.</li>
        <li>Metro 2579 is a mature product and suitable for experimental deployment.  
            Metro is the subject of on-going development and incompatible changes across milestone 
            builds are anticipated.</li>
      </ol>

      </subsection >

